01:38:28,116 --> 01:38:31,995
I NEVER FEEL ALONE
AMONG THE WAVES OF WRITING

1442
01:38:32,079 --> 01:38:36,291
MY FLAME WANTS TO SWIM TO THE OTHER SHORE

1443
01:38:48,804 --> 01:38:50,180
But I can see…

