01:38:51,515 --> 01:38:53,141
he did everything he wanted.

1445
01:38:54,977 --> 01:38:57,437
But seeing him again? No.

1446
01:39:02,901 --> 01:39:05,111
For the record,

1447
01:39:05,195 --> 01:39:06,655
my gratitude

1448
01:39:07,781 --> 01:39:09,199
is…

1449
01:39:12,828 --> 01:39:13,787
And…

1450
01:39:16,290 --> 01:39:18,542
I just want you to remember me a lot

1451
01:39:19,918 --> 01:39:20,836
and…

1452
01:39:29,636 --> 01:39:31,054
to laugh at me.
